    "markdown": "---\ntitle: Colophon\naliases:\n  - ../colophon.html\n  - ../r/colophon.html\n  - ../python/colophon.html\nengine: knitr\n---\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\nIn this appendix chapter, we provide details on the package versions used in this edition. We rendered the book with `quarto` [@quarto] and host it via GitHub Pages; the complete source is [available from GitHub](https://github.com/tidy-finance/website).\\index{GitHub} \\index{Quarto} \\index{Colophon} Select your language below to see the corresponding package versions.\n\n::: {.panel-tabset group=\"language\"}\n### R\n\nThis version of the book was built with R [@R-base] version 4\\.6\\.1 \\(2026\\-06\\-24\\, Happy Hop\\) and the following packages. We generated all R plots using `ggplot2` and its minimal theme (`theme_minimal()`).\\index{ggplot2 theme}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n`````{=html}\n<table class=\"table\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Package </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Version </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> RPostgres </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 1.4.10 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> RSQLite </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 3.53.3 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> broom </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 1.0.13 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> brulee </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 1.1.0 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> dbplyr </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 2.6.0 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> dplyr </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 1.2.1 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> fixest </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 0.14.2 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> fmpapi </td>\n   <td style=\"text-alig